{"tid":608231,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會將夢境同現實嘅事撈亂","createTime":"2018-03-28T03:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T11:46:42.000Z","uid":374,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"906cdf8b528d60d12ebc4c34bdb760b098fb04b9","tid":608231,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"有d簡單嘅野<br />\n譬如發夢見到嘅新聞<br />\n會唔小心同人講咗<br />\n後尾比人指正再自己查翻先知係夢入面嘅野<br />\n<br />\n同埋成日會將好真嘅夢入面<br />\n人地對我做過嘅事當做真係做過<br />\n搞到成日會誤會咗人<br />\n<br />\n宜家諗落呢樣野都幾危險<br />\n萬一有一日傾偈嗰陣講咗d不得了嘅嘢出黎<br />\n可能會影響自己份工/朋友關係<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有相似經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656428ee8f20d7bb7c9352bdd4bd4e63a8e66f62","tid":608231,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5223b1bc926551f26d83506814ffca10d0ccc2fa","tid":608231,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93e837664cf36c501dcfae6926ded24c43dc8a8","tid":608231,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a119ebb5e261038209be9657d26e540bcba96f","tid":608231,"uid":121844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"有病就要睇醫生唔好拖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0caf389bbca7c1a33f3ba2ab596602bdf14f2c7b","tid":608231,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"試過夢中夢中夢"},{"pid":"674b4d800823ba147f4d3ed2c493632171a5d9b0","tid":608231,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87a119ebb5e261038209be9657d26e540bcba96f","tid":608231,"uid":121844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"